data.name: label3.ToolTip
data.value:
Delay (milliseconds) only impacts spell casting timers.
Use 150 (default) if you're not sure.
If casting Stun takes 2.5 seconds then a 150 millisecond delay would shorten the casting timer bard to 2.35 seconds to accommodate for processing time.
Theoretically, a faster computer should require less of a delay.

data.name: label12.Text
data.value: Browse to the folder where this application was saved and open the 'GINAImportTriggers' folder. Select up to 14 .gtp files and click enter on your keyboard to run these files. Click Import in GINA up to 14 times until all triggers selected are imported. Repeat.
